content: ChristopherTrimboli: Focused on core feature development and dependency management, introducing ElizaOS Cloud as the default AI provider in the CLI (elizaos/eliza#6208) and executing a significant dependency update across the ecosystem (elizaos/eliza#6210). In addition to merging these two PRs, he supported the team by providing 4 code reviews. His work primarily involved modifications to configuration and test files, reflecting a focus on system health and testing alongside feature work.
